Minor update to the preceding;
Somehow, I managed to misplace a semicolon after "B >>= 8" in the ROUND macro, which prevents the patch I posted from compiling. With that obvious fix, I just verified that it passes the NBS Special Publication 500-20 test vectors. (Single-DES and triple-DES with 3 identical keys.)
