[CRYPTO] api: Fixed crypto_tfm context alignment
Previously the __aligned__ attribute was added to the crypto_tfm context member to ensure it is alinged correctly on architectures such as arm. Unfortunately kmalloc does not use the same minimum alignment rules as gcc so this is useless.
This patch changes it to use kmalloc's minimum alignment.
